## Summary

This documentation covers the Amplitude Experiment iOS SDK for client-side feature flag evaluation, including installation via CocoaPods/SPM, initialization with Amplitude Analytics or third-party integrations, remote evaluation via fetch(), local evaluation via start(), variant access, and exposure tracking with custom providers.

